<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Payment Setup Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #2d3748;
            background-color: #f7fafc;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #9568b0 0%, #7a5294 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 50px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><defs><pattern id="grain" width="100" height="100" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"><circle cx="50" cy="50" r="1" fill="white" opacity="0.1"/></pattern></defs><rect width="100" height="100" fill="url(%23grain)"/></svg>');
            opacity: 0.3;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 18px;
            opacity: 0.95;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 50px 40px;
        }
        
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a4cbd1 0%, #8bb8c0 100%);
            color: #2c5f73;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 35px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(164, 203, 209, 0.3);
        }
        
        .greeting {
            margin-bottom: 35px;
        }
        
        .greeting h2 {
            color: #9568b0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .greeting p {
            color: #4a5568;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        
        .amount-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #f1f3f4 100%);
            border-left: 5px solid #9568b0;
            padding: 35px;
            margin: 35px 0;
            border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .amount-section::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(149, 104, 176, 0.05) 0%, rgba(149, 104, 176, 0.02) 100%);
            border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0;
        }
        
        .amount-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .amount-row:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 2px solid rgba(149, 104, 176, 0.2);
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        
        .amount-label {
            color: #718096;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .amount-value {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2d3748;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .total-amount {
            color: #9568b0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .info-section {
            margin: 35px 0;
        }
        
        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 15px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .info-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .info-label {
            min-width: 140px;
            color: #718096;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        
        .info-value {
            color: #2d3748;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .setup-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #f1f3f4 100%);
            padding: 35px;
            margin: 35px 0;
            border-radius: 12px;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .setup-section::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(149, 104, 176, 0.05) 0%, rgba(149, 104, 176, 0.02) 100%);
            border-radius: 12px;
        }
        
        .setup-section h3 {
            color: #9568b0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .setup-list {
            list-style: none;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .setup-list li {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding-left: 35px;
            position: relative;
            color: #4a5568;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .setup-list li:before {
            content: "✓";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            color: #9568b0;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
            background: rgba(149, 104, 176, 0.1);
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        
        .important-note {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff5f5 0%, #fed7d7 100%);
            border-left: 5px solid #f56565;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 35px 0;
            border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0;
        }
        
        .important-note h4 {
            color: #c53030;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .important-note p {
            color: #c53030;
            font-size: 15px;
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #f1f3f4 100%);
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            color: #718096;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        .footer .highlight {
            color: #9568b0;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .footer .contact-info {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                margin: 0;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
            
            .header {
                padding: 40px 25px;
            }
            
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 28px;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 35px 25px;
            }
            
            .amount-section {
                padding: 25px;
            }
            
            .info-row {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                padding: 12px 0;
            }
            
            .info-label {
                min-width: auto;
                margin-bottom: 8px;
            }
            
            .setup-section {
                padding: 25px;
            }
            
            .footer {
                padding: 30px 25px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Payment Setup Complete</h1>
            <p>Your payment method has been securely saved</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="status-badge">Payment Method Saved</div>
            
            <div class="greeting">
                <h2>Hello {{customerName}},</h2>
                <p>Great! Your payment method has been successfully set up and saved securely. Your move is now confirmed and ready to proceed.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="amount-section">
                <div class="amount-row">
                    <span class="amount-label">Total Amount:</span>
                    <span class="amount-value total-amount">£{{totalAmount}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="amount-row">
                    <span class="amount-label">Payment Status:</span>
                    <span class="amount-value">Payment Setup</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-section">
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Quote Reference:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">#{{quoteReference}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Setup Date:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{setupDate}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Setup Time:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{setupTime}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="setup-section">
                <h3>What Happens Next?</h3>
                <ul class="setup-list">
                    <li>We'll contact you within 24 hours to confirm your moving details</li>
                    <li>Your payment method will be charged on the day of your move</li>
                    <li>You'll receive a reminder 48 hours before your move</li>
                    <li>Payment will be processed automatically on move day</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="important-note">
                <h4>Important Information</h4>
                <p>Your payment method will be charged the full amount (£{{totalAmount}}) on the day of your move. Please ensure your payment method has sufficient funds available on the scheduled date.</p>
            </div>
            
            <p style="color: #4a5568; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">If you need to update your payment method or modify your booking, please contact us as soon as possible. Changes made within 48 hours of your move may incur additional charges.</p>
            
            <p style="color: #9568b0; font-weight: 600; font-size: 18px; margin-top: 25px;">Thank you for choosing Tranzr Moves!</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><span class="highlight">Tranzr Moves</span> - Professional moving services across the United Kingdom</p>
            <div class="contact-info">
                <p>Email: support@tranzrmoves.com | Phone: +44 (0) 20 1234 5678</p>
                <p>© {{currentYear}} Tranzr Moves. All rights reserved.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
